                                     c.     Photocopy of the certification of good moral character issued by

                                            the college guidance counselor/college registrar;


                                     d.     Photocopy of checklist of course;

                                     e.     Photocopy of pre-registration form;

                                     f.     1 pc. 2x2 colored picture (any background color);

                                     g.     1 pcs. short ordinary folder;

