                              from the University Personnel;


                                     (For CvSu Scholarship Privilege applicants only)

                       e.     Photocopy of certification as Barangay Officials/SK Officials from the Department

                                         of Interior and Local Government;

                                     (For  RA  7160  (dependents  of  barangay  officials  and  SK  officials

                              applicants only)

                       B. For Graduate Students

                              The applicants must submit the following:


                              1.     Accomplished application form for scholarship;

                              2.     Photocopy of Transcript of Records;

                              3.     Photocopy of birth certificate (if unmarried);

                              4.     Photocopy of marriage contract;

                              5.     Photocopy of checklist of course;




